sequenceDiagram
  participant AgentLoop as Agent Loop
  participant R as Scoped Retrieval
  participant KB as Knowledge Sources
  participant Snap as Snapshot Store
  participant M as Model

  AgentLoop->>R: request(scope, asOf)
  R->>KB: recall candidates within scope
  KB-->>R: candidates + versions
  R->>R: filter/rerank/trim/cite
  R->>Snap: write audit snapshot
  Snap-->>R: snapshotId
  R-->>AgentLoop: context items + snapshotId
  AgentLoop->>M: model input references snapshotId
